<h2>2. Choose a Reliable Crypto Exchange</h2>
  
<p>In 2025, picking the right <a href="https://www.psx.com.pk/" rel="noopener">crypto exchange</a> is more important than ever, as new regulations and emerging platforms change the landscape. Look for exchanges that offer advanced security measures like multi-factor authentication (MFA), cold storage for funds, and have low trading fees. The most popular exchanges in 2025 might include Binance, Coinbase, Kraken, and decentralized exchanges (DEXs) like Uniswap and PancakeSwap.</p>

<h3>2.1 Factors to Consider When Choosing an Exchange</h3>
<ul>
